text: Better than expected (given ave 3.7 ratings). Enjoyed the Sarawak laksa. Thick broth and I added minced meat.
I ordered dry black kolo mee. It was quite good with lean tasty char siew but the mee was a bit too sweet. In future I'll try other types of the kolo mee.

Another addition of Sarawak Delicacy in a new town. Maintaining the spread of original Sarawak everyday staple to some new creations. Excellent food & excellent service. So proud for them to expand their love of spreading Sarawak traditional eatüëçüëç
